                    <h2 class="mb-4" style="font-size: 50px; color: #fff;"><i class="fas fa-skull" style="margin-right: 20px;"></i>The origins of survival games</h2>
                    <h5 style="margin: 40px 0 20px 0; font-size: 30px; color: #fff;">In 50's</h5>
                    <p>
                        Survival game was originally from Midwest of United States in early 50's.
                        <br>Midwest of United States was animal husbandry center at that time and in order to facilitate the Cowboys for easy managing cattle or horses, someone invented a gun with color marked bullets, so with a different color shells for the livestock.  Later, a group of naughty cowboys, starting with colored shooting gun to each other and by hit body losing the game and must buy a case of beers for the winner, so the final winner as a survivor could win several cases of beers, that's how Survival Game got name from.
                    </p>
                    <h5 style="margin: 40px 0 20px 0; font-size: 30px; color: #fff;">In 70~80's</h5>
                    <p>Japan started a Airsoft Game which used airsoft guns mainly and the used guns were designed to closely emulate the real gun as possible and the combat & playing concepts were very similar to Survival Game and it became a sort of recreational hobby or leisure spreading all over the world, including Taiwan.</p>
                </div>
